<br>
What does help, always, is experience with doing EQ scripted events and boss mob encounters.  There's a whole set of basic raid tactics that we all learned on the way to the elementals - corner the mob, or don't, depending on circumstance, use kite teams, hide the casters behind things, tank the adds, mez the adds, give the adds a quarter and send them for chewing gum...<br>
<br>
If you don't have the basic skills, it doesn't matter if your raid leader is sleeping with Absor.  Not that Absor knows shit about shit anyway... <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=366694">Nayl</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
